com.homesky.homecloud_lib

Class HomecloudWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.homesky.homecloud_lib.HomecloudWrapper

  • public class HomecloudWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    A wrapper for the Homecloud class that adds method synchronization to allow usage on multi-threaded applications.
